		"description": "{html}<div><p>Basically, if the scrollview is zoomed enabled, when you zoom in\nand rotated the device, the scrollView is moved to the left and top\nof the screen. It does not stay where it is set to stay, even if\nthe left, top, bottom, and right properties are set to 0. You'll\nfind a working sample attached.</p>\n<p>Referring to HD ticket: <a href=\n\"http://developer.appcelerator.com/helpdesk/view/69971\">http://developer.appcelerator.com/helpdesk/view/69971</a></p>\n<p>Tested on iPad Simulator 4.2<br>\nTi SDK 1.6 (Feb 1 2011 17:47 ra6320820)</p></div>{html}",
